tak se tak nenuť do úsměvu.

333
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:43,740
Tak to není.

334
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:45,540
Já...

335
00:15:45,680 --> 00:15:48,880
♪ Hong Do-ya.

336
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:52,620
♪ Neplač.

337
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:59,300
♪ Hee Kyung je tady.

338
00:15:59,420 --> 00:15:59,780
Oh!

339
